description:
Fast effective relief from indigestion and heartburn.

Rennie is an antacid that provides fast relief from indigestion, heartburn, acidity and dyspepsia.

When symptoms strike, Rennie quickly gets to work to relieve painful symptoms so you can get on with your life.

- Fast effective relief from indigestion heartburn, acidity and dyspepsia.

- Neutralises stomach acid to relieve pain and discomfort.

- Great tasting spearmint flavour

- Suitable for use during pregnancy

- Taken day or night to relieve heartburn and indigestion fast
